      license-feature-version="1.14.0.qualifier">

   <description url="https://www.cevelop.com/features">
      The Constificator is an Eclipse CDT plugin that is able to decide
if a variable, a function parameter or a member function can
be const qualified. If so, it will offer an appropriate quickfix
or refactoring.
   </description>

